      { id: "weath15", spanish: "El clima esta loco", english: "The weather is crazy", difficulty: "hard", example: "The weather is absolutely crazy today! First sunshine then rain now hail! I have never seen this!", exampleTranslation: "El clima esta absolutamente loco hoy! Primero sol luego lluvia ahora granizo! Nunca he visto esto!" }
